{
  "texts": [
    "The data is sampled from the mid-section of these blocks and is organized into two datasets (large and small).",
    "The large dataset covers cubes with large pores (0.4 mm, 0.5 mm, and 0.6 mm) and the small dataset covers cubes with small pores (0.05 mm and 0.1 mm).",
    "The three Asphalt datasets were originally described in Souza (2018) and donated by the author of that paper.",
    "Accelerometer data was collected on a smartphone installed inside a vehicle using a flexible suction holder near the dashboard.",
    "The acceleration forces are given by the accelerometer sensor of the device and are the data used for The Colposcopy data is described in Gutiérrez-Fragoso et al. (2017) and was donated to the repository by the authors foot_5."
  ]
}